description: Fram Skandinavien AB engages in the investment and establishment of new companies within information technology (IT) and online marketing in Scandinavia and Southeast Asia. The company is headquartered in Stockholm, Stockholm. The company went IPO on 2017-10-12. The Company’s operations comprise two segments: Venture Building, which implies investment in technology companies and an operational support to founders of such enterprises; and Standing Teams that implies IT-development operations carried out mainly for Northern European and Southeast Asia clients. The Company’s approach is a long-term partnership with customers within web development, mobile development areas, as well as within those areas related to big data and artificial intelligence. Fram Skandinavien AB (publ) operates a wholly-owned subsidiary Fram Ltd, based and operational in Vietnam. The Company’s main shareholder is Norsel Industries BV.
